caption.p: Electrolyte leakage of three cultivars (‘Rowa‘, ‘Półdługa‘, ‘Krakowianka‘) of radish seeds ( Raphanus sativus L.) treatment of aqueous extracts from Solidago canadensis L. leaves; mean values ± SD ( n = 10) with different letter (a–f) differ statistically according to Duncan test at p < 0.05.
